    • Method Detail

      • valueOf

        public static Language valueOf(int languageId)
        Factory convenience method.
        Constructs a new Language-Object with the short language name.
        Like 'de' for German. Language.getLanguageShort(int language).
        If the id is out range a Language Object with Language.L_ALL will be constructed.
        Parameters:
        languageId - the specific language-id, see the constants in this class.
